title: [Marble Springs, Cobbled Path]
description: The cool, refreshing scent of the river to the south is strong here, its natural odor carried along by a light breeze.  A few black oak trees overshadow the path, their broad trunks obscuring the rocky shore beyond.  A couple of red-tiled roofs peek through the leafy branches.
